+/**
+ * drm_scdc_writeb - write a single byte to SCDC
+ * @adap: ddc adapter
+ * @offset: offset of register to read
+ * @value: return location for the register value
+ *
+ * Writes a single byte to SCDC. This is a convenience wrapper around the
